### Notes

 As the Author strange to Vanilla combat system, Weapon Stats for Vanilla version may not so banlanced.  

### FAQ    

 Q1: CE compatible?    
 A1: CE compatible!    

 Q2: All Texture issues including but not limited to: "Texture style Non-conformant", "Ugly", etc.    
 A2: The author may draw/optimize Textures later... but now He just want to stretch 464 hours into 889 hours.    
 Q3: Why Powered-weapons were arranged into Pulse-charged munition tech? It was a melee weapon.    
 A3: The author want to keep research tab clean and simple, def as less research item as possible.    

 Q4: These Powered weapons are too expensive, I'd rather to buy monosword with this money.    
 A4: Bro, Powered weapons ensured the ability of stably self-supplying High-ArmorPiercing weapons on Colony its own, after all, it may not always be possible to buy monosword-like weapon.    

**("Starter Part" Above.)**        
**(If this is the first time using this mod, you can stop reading at here and just goto play the "Rimworld" now.)**

